Feature / Aspect LlamaIndex LangChain
Primary Focus Data indexing & retrieval (RAG systems) Workflow orchestration & agent-based AI systems
Embedding Use Case Embeds documents for semantic search & retrieval Embeddings used within chains or agents for reasoning & context
Embedding Workflow Simple: Load Chunk Embed Index Query Complex: Embed Integrate into chains Use in multi-step workflows
Supported Data Types PDFs, text, web pages, structured data Text, APIs, databases, external tools
Vector DB Integration Pinecone, Weaviate, Chroma, Qdrant (optimized) Pinecone, FAISS, Chroma, custom integrations
Embedding Performance Fast (50100ms for similarity search) [markaicode.com] Slower (due to multi-step workflows, 25s per tool call) [markaicode.com]
Learning Curve Gentle, quick setup Steeper, requires understanding chains, agents, tools
Use Case Scope Narrow: Document QA, knowledge bases, semantic search Broad: Chatbots, agents, automation, decision-making
Modularity Focused modules for indexing and querying Highly modular: chains, agents, tools, memory
Embedding Customization Chunking strategies, similarity tuning, top-k retrieval Prompt tuning, agent reasoning, embedding routing
Community & Ecosystem 34k+ GitHub stars, growing ecosystem 87k+ GitHub stars, extensive integrations (700+)
Cost Efficiency Lower compute & API usage for retrieval Higher API usage due to multi-step workflows
Scalability Excellent for read-heavy workloads (1M+ docs) [markaicode.com] Good for agent pools, but memory grows with complexity
Hybrid Usage Can be used as a retrieval tool inside LangChain agents Can orchestrate LlamaIndex queries within broader workflows
Best For Fast, accurate document search & QA Complex reasoning, multi-agent systems, tool integration
